**/*.py[cod]
**/.pytest_cache
**/.mypy_cache
**/.ruff_cache
**/.hypothesis
**/*.egg-info
dist
build
docs
research
*.md
.env
.env.*
cortexward-baseline.json
sbom.cdx.json
coverage.xml
.coverage
